title: Homomorphic Encryption for Ocean Market
body:
Homomorphic Encryption based solution to preserve intellectual property and/or privacy of monetized data for participant X and AT THE SAME TIME preserve intellectual property and/or privacy of the monetized algorithm/model applied on that data for participant Y for applications in healthcare and finance.

## Full Proposal
https://port.oceanprotocol.com/t/grant-proposal-homomorphic-encryption-for-ocean-market/816

## Grant Deliverables
[ ] Detailed specification of the use-case in healthcare or finance
[ ] “Encryption module” provided as open-source software for homomorphic encryption of datasets for the Ocean Market
[ ] “Inference module” provided as open-source software for computation/inference based on Homomorphic Encrypted datasets of the Ocean Market
[ ] “App” provided as open-source solution which integrates and makes previous deliverables accessible via https://ocean-he.tributech.io 2 for an E2E-demonstration of Homomorphic Encryption on Ocean Market
